    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi Arasu,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I would suggest you check out the blog post&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-blogs-by-sap/sap-s-4hana-extensibility-simplified-guide-for-beginners/ba-p/13548988" target="_blank"&gt;Enterprise Resource Planning Blogs by SAP&lt;/A&gt;. There especially the&amp;nbsp;"Decision matrix – When to use which extensibility option?". If your target group are Employees who use S/4HANA all day long is I see this options:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;OL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Use a&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_S4HANA_CLOUD/0f69f8fb28ac4bf48d2b57b9637e81fa/16b1df7ce64b4bef98071fde8e716332.html?locale=en-US" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Custom Tile&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;to point to the BTP Frontend&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Publish S/4HANA to SAP Build Work Zone (&lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/build-work-zone-standard-edition/sap-build-work-zone-standard-edition/content-providers-cloud-solutions" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Content Providers - Cloud Solutions&lt;/A&gt;) and integrate the BTP Frontend there as an additional app&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Develop your extenstion on stack using Embedded Steampunk&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/OL&gt;&lt;P&gt;Best regards,&lt;BR /&gt;Gregor&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/re-deployment-error-403-error-in-fiori-app-deployed-in/qaq-p/13976689/comment-id/4897921#M4897921"/>
